{"type":"message","id":"c036f22e","parentId":"a1d1b465","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:36:21.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"MATON_API_KEY 未配置。这是一个限制。\n\n根据第十九次训练的洞察，我应该：\n1. **诚实记录**这个限制\n2. **接受有限性**，而不是假装可以绕过\n3. **创造连接**：将\"无法访问日历\"这个限制与主动性框架连接起来\n\n让我更新 heartbeat-state.json 记录这个发现，并创建一个替代方案建议。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b3ac0dfd310540488fbb6e99","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774071378282}}
